{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2016-11-03-wolframalpha-and-pokmon-answers","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"kevinhakanson.com","author":"Kevin Hakanson"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c2cb3595-ae89-5319-9350-e6c469e94821","excerpt":"The other day, my daughter had me search for zigzagoon on Wolfram|Alpha: Computational Knowledge Engine.  Apparently, there is a full Pokédex loaded because it…","html":"<p>The other day, my daughter had me search for <a href=\"https://www.wolframalpha.com/input/?i=zigzagoon\">zigzagoon</a> on <a href=\"https://www.wolframalpha.com/\">Wolfram|Alpha: Computational Knowledge Engine</a>.  Apparently, there is a full Pokédex loaded because it knew details like number, type, size, and generation.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 350px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/03dd1b11447860ddc0de24a04dd2a714/d6f3f/pastedImage_6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 106%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Input Interpretation: Zigzagoon\"\n        title=\"Input Interpretation: Zigzagoon\"\n        src=\"/static/03dd1b11447860ddc0de24a04dd2a714/d6f3f/pastedImage_6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/03dd1b11447860ddc0de24a04dd2a714/00d96/pastedImage_6.png 148w,\n/static/03dd1b11447860ddc0de24a04dd2a714/0b23c/pastedImage_6.png 295w,\n/static/03dd1b11447860ddc0de24a04dd2a714/d6f3f/pastedImage_6.png 350w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>So, I tried this computation…</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b55710b47e53c748d3c5c2577b1f2b9d/f9552/pastedImage_4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 7.7039274924471295%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAXUlEQVQI143JQQtAMAAFYP//J8m4uG+TZXZxwUbSsChlz0o5yuHrvd6LnGHYNIXT7HWMRUiKfeC4rARWBf9TpCVBLxOYOkUr4tAJ5iZHV4VNZTgnDiwC3paB+PD8N72gk7Up3GgTAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"average height of generation iii pokemon\"\n        title=\"average height of generation iii pokemon\"\n        src=\"/static/b55710b47e53c748d3c5c2577b1f2b9d/799d3/pastedImage_4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b55710b47e53c748d3c5c2577b1f2b9d/00d96/pastedImage_4.png 148w,\n/static/b55710b47e53c748d3c5c2577b1f2b9d/0b23c/pastedImage_4.png 295w,\n/static/b55710b47e53c748d3c5c2577b1f2b9d/799d3/pastedImage_4.png 590w,\n/static/b55710b47e53c748d3c5c2577b1f2b9d/f9552/pastedImage_4.png 662w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>and it worked as expected!</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 283px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bf0a345159bf4130edf866d768e6b1c0/9cedd/pastedImage_5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 97.87985865724382%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Input Interpretation: Generation III Pokémon height\"\n        title=\"Input Interpretation: Generation III Pokémon height\"\n        src=\"/static/bf0a345159bf4130edf866d768e6b1c0/9cedd/pastedImage_5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bf0a345159bf4130edf866d768e6b1c0/00d96/pastedImage_5.png 148w,\n/static/bf0a345159bf4130edf866d768e6b1c0/9cedd/pastedImage_5.png 283w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 283px) 100vw, 283px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>How is this relevant to the capabilities we are developing around how knowledge workers <strong>Find</strong>, <strong>Analyze</strong>, and <strong>Decide</strong> about <strong>Content</strong>?  Now think again about the Wolfram|Alpha Pokémon example and how that combines natural language input and content to recommend an answer.  Then go to <a href=\"https://www.wolframalpha.com/\">https://www.wolframalpha.com/</a> and try some queries out yourself.  How does the user experience compare to more traditional research products?</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Wolfram|Alpha and Pokémon Answers","date":"November 03, 2016","tags":["random","nlp","pokemon"]}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/2016-11-03-wolframalpha-and-pokmon-answers","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2016-10-17-ux-issues-with-authenticator-apps"},"frontmatter":{"tags":["ux","mfa"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2016-